quran[7{c,v,t}:
3,16,"yeh woh log hain, jo kehte hain ke"" maalik! hum imaan laaye, hamari khataon se Dur guzar farma aur hamein aatish dozakh se bacha le """
3,17,"yeh log sabr karne walay hain, rasbaazhain, farmanbardar aur Fayaz hain aur raat ki aakhri gharion mein Allah se mughfirat ki duayen manga karte hain"
3,18,"Allah ne khud shahadat di hai ke is ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai, o ray ( yahi shahadat ) firshton aur sab ahal ilm ne bhi di hai woh insaaf par qaim hai uss zabardast hakeem ke siwa fi al waqea koi khuda nahi hai"
3,19,"Allah ke nazdeek deen sirf islam hai is deen se hatt kar jo mukhtalif tareeqay unn logon ne ikhtiyar kiye, jinhein kitaab di gayi thi, unn ke iss tarz amal ki koi wajah is ke siwa nah thi ke unhon ne ilm aa jaane ke baad aapas mein aik dosray par zayad-ti karne ke liye aisa kya aur jo koi Allah ke ehkaam o Hadayat ki itaat se inkaar kar day, Allah ko is se hisaab letay kuch der nahi lagti hai"
3,20,"ab agar yeh log tum se jhagra karen, tawa noon se kaho :"" mein ne aur mere pairwoo-n (maan-nay walonn )ne to Allah ke agay sir tasleem khham kar diya hai"" phir ahal kitaab aur ghair ahal kitaab dono se pucho :"" kya tum ne bhi is ki itaat o bandagi qubool ki ?"" agar ki to woh raah raast pa gay, aur agar is se mun morra to tum par sirf pegham pouncha dainay ki zimma daari thi agay Allah khud apne bundon ke mamlaat dekhnay wala hai"
3,21,"jo log Allah ke ehkaam o Hadayat ko maan-ne se inkaar karte hain aur is ke payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal karte hain aur aisay logon ki jaan ke darpay ho jatay hain, jo Khalq khuda mein Adal o raasti ka hukum dainay ke liye utheen, un ko dard naak saza ki khush khaberi suna do"
3,22,"yeh woh log hain jin ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein zaya hogaye, aur un ka madadgaar koi nahi hai"
